data.description: Walking Distance to the water! Updated home near Lake Texoma on almost an acre! Plenty of room to spread out and bring all your lake toys or RV. Sit on your large front porch and enjoy the lake life! This little gem has updated flooring, paint, roof, HVAC, Electrical panel, light fixtures, dishwasher and hot water heater! Large family room with additional living space that could be large dining area. Kitchen is good sized with breakfast area! All bedrooms are oversized!  30 x 40 Shop with 2 large garage doors. Electricity and water in shop. Office space or possible living quarters in shop. Paradise cove and all it's amenities are less than 5 minutes away!
